List of helper scripts:

add_frontend_port_forwarding.py
  Enable ip forwarding on frontend server, so that backend servers could visit the Internet.

list_all_installed_deb_packages.py
  List all the installed .deb packages in a system.

ssh_nopass_cleanup.rb
  Delete duplicate entries in "authorized_keys" file. It will backup the original file to "authorized_keys~".

ssh_nopass_all2all.rb
  Configure ssh nopass visiting in a cluster.

make_tar.py
  Create a tar.gz package for nova. It will be placed at nova source code root.

